  glib-networking-2.30.1-r1.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #393007

  18 Jan 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  glib-networking-2.30.1-r1.ebuild, glib-networking-2.30.2.ebuild:
